headline: Deputy Field Office Director at U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE)

defaultPosition.description: Lead multiple teams through subordinate managers in the San Diego area of responsibility by providing oversight of the Imperial Regional Detention Facility, the Otay Mesa Detention Center and San Diego Operations, which includes juvenile and travel processing.  To accomplish this I use my extensive knowledge of immigration enforcement and operations procedures and standards to remove aliens from the United States through fair and effective enforcement of immigration laws.
defaultPosition.title: Deputy Field Office Director

positions.description: Lead multiple teams through subordinate managers in the San Diego area of responsibility by providing oversight of the Imperial Regional Detention Facility, the Otay Mesa Detention Center and San Diego Operations, which includes juvenile and travel processing.  To accomplish this I use my extensive knowledge of immigration enforcement and operations procedures and standards to remove aliens from the United States through fair and effective enforcement of immigration laws.
positions.title: Deputy Field Office Director

positions.description: Provided leadership and operational direction to 24 Field Offices and accompanying Areas of Responsibility (AOR) located throughout the United States and its territories, which encompass 190 sub-offices and over 6,500 employees.  Ensured the proper employment of resources to arrest fugitive and criminal aliens, detaining certain aliens, and removing them from the United States through fair and effective enforcement of immigration laws.
positions.title: Deputy Assistant Director

positions.description: Led multiple teams through subordinate managers at more than 11 locations throughout the states of Washington, Oregon, and Alaska.  Utilized expert knowledge of immigration enforcement and operations procedures and standards to manage complex enforcement and removal programs, as well as a large-scale federal and contract detention operations.
positions.title: Assitant Field Office Director

positions.description: Provided leadership and operational direction and oversight to six offices located throughout the state of Washington comprised of over 120 personnel providing adjudication services to the residents of Washington and Northern Idaho.
positions.title: District Director
